subject: Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race (Alaska)
Dog Sledding
lead_paragraph: A party atmosphere swirled around Anchorage, Alaska, at the start of the Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race on Saturday, when 67 mushers and more than 1,000 dogs set their sights for Nome.
